title: I have a Pixel 4A and call all my contacts but one! Their phone will not ring but I hear ringing on
content: I have a Pixel 4A and can call all my contacts but one! Their phone will not ring but I hear ringing on my end and I am able to leave a message on their phone which they can see! The reverse is true also, when they call me they hear a ring and can leave a message.  I do not hear a ring and one difference is I do not see the message they left me!
